data.description: Come see this beautiful single story home on a greenbelt with all the bells and whistles! Gorgeous open floor plan with secluded primary suite and tray ceilings. So many upgrades! This home includes granite countertops, crown molding, wood-look tile floors, a whole house 24 kw GENERAC generator, solar screens, an "Elfa" system in the master closet, and so much more! The neighborhood boasts wonderful amenities including pool, playground, trails and more. Just a couple minutes to the elementary school. Welcome home!
